entries.femaleVariant: Hey, V. Got a serious gig, which means I'll be needing a serious merc.
Want you to hop to 6th Street turf and graft a virus onto their tech. Counting on you, champ.
Oh, and one last thing – there's this techie, Lucius Thoran. And I wouldn't mind if he got a piece of lead to the skull – ya dig? Good. Spec's attached.
